data.description: Discover the ideal ranch home in Newnan just minutes from downtown shopping and dining. This home features a lovely family room with hardwood floors, vaulted ceiling, and floor to ceiling stone fireplace. The cozy kitchen with view of private backyard features an eat-in area and a large utility room. Enjoy the master bedroom equipped with a charming bay window, en suite bathroom with separate tub/shower, and walk-in closet. Two secondary bedrooms share the full hall bathroom. Outside, a back deck offers serene views of the secluded backyard, complete with an outbuilding.
